-; 224: xmm15
-; 240: gs:0x08,   stack base  (highest address)
-; 248: gs:0x10,   stack limit (lowest address)
-; 256: gs:0x1478, stack guarantee (deallocation stack)  
-; 264: gs:0x20,   fiber data                            
